1
00:01:37,920 --> 00:01:40,990
[The Epoch of Miyu]

2
00:01:41,050 --> 00:01:43,970
[Episode 3]

3
00:02:25,670 --> 00:02:28,829
These days, I keep telling myself

4
00:02:29,710 --> 00:02:31,510
that after 10 years of marriage,

5
00:02:32,070 --> 00:02:33,240
the bond between us

6
00:02:33,240 --> 00:02:35,190
can't be broken so easily.

7
00:02:36,329 --> 00:02:37,800
This is just a small episode

8
00:02:37,800 --> 00:02:39,079
in our marriage.

9
00:02:40,710 --> 00:02:42,710
Maybe if we had a child,

10
00:02:43,840 --> 00:02:46,079
or if his career was better,

11
00:02:47,680 --> 00:02:51,079
we would be better able to weather
the storms of our marriage.

12
00:02:51,360 --> 00:02:52,560
Life

13
00:02:53,310 --> 00:02:54,590
has to go on.

14
00:03:12,320 --> 00:03:13,000
Hello?

15
00:03:16,480 --> 00:03:17,360
It's today?

16
00:03:19,840 --> 00:03:22,170
Tell Director Wang we'll be there on time.

17
00:03:23,680 --> 00:03:24,430
Gotta go.

18
00:03:28,910 --> 00:03:29,910
Did I wake you up?

19
00:03:31,350 --> 00:03:32,470
I need to go to Ningxin.

20
00:03:32,470 --> 00:03:33,930
I have to leave right away.

21
00:03:37,450 --> 00:03:40,370
Is there any progress
on the project from last time?

22
00:03:40,470 --> 00:03:41,400
I'm not sure yet.

23
00:03:41,710 --> 00:03:43,570
I'll go check it out first and see.

24
00:03:43,610 --> 00:03:45,620
Why don't you eat breakfast
before leaving?

25
00:03:45,620 --> 00:03:46,750
I'll make it for you.

26
00:03:50,110 --> 00:03:52,280
Number 33, Xu Miyu,

27
00:03:52,280 --> 00:03:54,910
Xu Miyu.
Please proceed to Examination Room 4.

28
00:03:53,610 --> 00:03:54,140
[Obstetric First Visit Form]

29
00:03:54,140 --> 00:03:55,460
[Mingmei Obstetrics and Gynecology Hospital
Ultrasound Examination Report]

30
00:03:56,680 --> 00:03:58,820
Mingmei Obstetrics and Gynecology Hospital
CBC Report

31
00:04:02,440 --> 00:04:03,630
Don't be nervous.

32
00:04:05,150 --> 00:04:05,670
[Mingmei Obstetrics and Gynecology Hospital
Ultrasound Examination Report]

33
00:04:05,670 --> 00:04:06,670
[Ultrasound Findings]

34
00:04:06,700 --> 00:04:08,360
[Ultrasound findings: uterine fibroids
and a right adnexal cystic mass.]

35
00:04:15,810 --> 00:04:16,709
It's fine.

36
00:04:16,790 --> 00:04:19,399
Since you get regular checkups,
it should be fine.

37
00:04:19,399 --> 00:04:20,790
This fibroid

38
00:04:20,810 --> 00:04:23,210
is like a pimple on your face.

39
00:04:23,340 --> 00:04:24,690
It won't affect anything.

40
00:04:24,690 --> 00:04:27,320
But I still want to have
a minimally invasive procedure.

41
00:04:27,320 --> 00:04:28,640
That way I will feel more at ease.

42
00:04:28,640 --> 00:04:29,930
Why do you have to make

43
00:04:30,080 --> 00:04:32,500
several cuts in your belly?

44
00:04:32,800 --> 00:04:35,060
I've been trying to get pregnant lately,

45
00:04:35,120 --> 00:04:36,400
but it has not been going well.

46
00:04:36,400 --> 00:04:38,060
Don't put so much pressure on yourself.

47
00:04:38,060 --> 00:04:39,350
A lot of women

48
00:04:39,409 --> 00:04:42,120
keep looking for problems in themselves,

49
00:04:42,310 --> 00:04:43,120
and in the end,

50
00:04:43,290 --> 00:04:44,830
there is nothing wrong at all.

51
00:04:44,830 --> 00:04:45,800
Just relax.

52
00:04:47,310 --> 00:04:48,370
Thank you, doctor.

53
00:04:51,000 --> 00:04:51,830
Well...

54
00:05:03,680 --> 00:05:04,360
Miyu,

55
00:05:05,010 --> 00:05:06,740
which one do you like best here?

56
00:05:06,750 --> 00:05:08,010
This one is beautiful.

57
00:05:09,020 --> 00:05:11,400
Actually, I'm not an expert in jewelry,

58
00:05:11,470 --> 00:05:14,450
but if I have to choose,

59
00:05:14,630 --> 00:05:15,810
I would pick this one.

60
00:05:15,810 --> 00:05:16,740
Why?

61
00:05:16,920 --> 00:05:17,750
I value

62
00:05:17,750 --> 00:05:19,630
the reputation of this bracelet's owner.

63
00:05:19,630 --> 00:05:22,240
She should be Ms. Fang Yahui,

64
00:05:22,240 --> 00:05:23,720
a Chinese antique collector.

65
00:05:23,720 --> 00:05:25,950
And although it wasn't made
by a famous master,

66
00:05:25,950 --> 00:05:28,270
I think it's very pure,

67
00:05:28,270 --> 00:05:29,720
the texture is smooth,

68
00:05:29,870 --> 00:05:32,200
and it has the qualities of Zhengkun jade.

69
00:05:32,680 --> 00:05:33,390
How did

70
00:05:33,390 --> 00:05:35,159
that red-glazed vase
Miyu picked for you last time

71
00:05:35,159 --> 00:05:36,070
turn out?

72
00:05:36,430 --> 00:05:37,950
Its market price has doubled.

73
00:05:37,950 --> 00:05:38,720
So?

74
00:05:38,840 --> 00:05:40,440
Miyu knows her stuff, right?

75
00:05:40,750 --> 00:05:43,710
Don't be fooled by her quiet,
domestic side;

76
00:05:43,800 --> 00:05:45,070
she's actually keeping her talents
under wraps.

77
00:05:45,070 --> 00:05:46,200
She's very capable.

78
00:05:46,560 --> 00:05:47,680
That impressive?

79
00:05:48,070 --> 00:05:50,000
It's a real waste of your talents
that you're not

80
00:05:50,000 --> 00:05:51,630
an art appraisal expert.

81
00:05:52,800 --> 00:05:54,430
Are you asking her to do the hard work?

82
00:05:54,430 --> 00:05:56,270
With a husband who dotes on her like that,

83
00:05:56,270 --> 00:05:57,670
it would break his heart.

84
00:05:57,770 --> 00:05:58,190
Yes.

85
00:05:58,750 --> 00:06:00,410
I'll take this jade bracelet.

86
00:06:03,980 --> 00:06:04,820
Yucheng

87
00:06:04,890 --> 00:06:08,350
usually relies on the support
of all of your husbands.

88
00:06:08,370 --> 00:06:11,160
I can't be of much help
with other matters.

89
00:06:12,250 --> 00:06:13,480
If any of you ladies think

90
00:06:13,480 --> 00:06:15,250
I have some talent

91
00:06:15,430 --> 00:06:17,000
in appraising treasures,

92
00:06:18,390 --> 00:06:19,920
feel free to call on me anytime.

93
00:06:19,920 --> 00:06:21,850
I certainly won't hesitate to ask.

94
00:06:24,020 --> 00:06:25,820
I'm going to the restroom first.

95
00:06:26,160 --> 00:06:27,130
I'll go too.

96
00:06:27,150 --> 00:06:28,410
You two keep chatting.

97
00:06:32,190 --> 00:06:33,920
Yucheng was discovered
and promoted

98
00:06:33,920 --> 00:06:35,480
by Mr. Hu, who has a keen eye for talent.

99
00:06:35,480 --> 00:06:37,750
Now that he's at a critical stage
in his career,

100
00:06:37,750 --> 00:06:39,390
he needs Mr. Hu's guidance.

101
00:06:42,270 --> 00:06:43,870
I heard your Nie Yucheng

102
00:06:44,310 --> 00:06:45,750
has a project lately

103
00:06:45,770 --> 00:06:47,430
that's giving him a headache.

104
00:06:49,020 --> 00:06:51,220
I don't ask too much about his work,

105
00:06:51,520 --> 00:06:53,570
But I did hear that

106
00:06:53,600 --> 00:06:55,930
Mr. Hu assigned him a very important task.

107
00:06:56,040 --> 00:06:58,030
We must thank Mr. Hu for his trust.

108
00:06:58,240 --> 00:06:59,550
There's no need for that.
Don't be too formal.

109
00:06:59,550 --> 00:07:01,150
No, we really must thank you.

110
00:07:03,610 --> 00:07:04,200
By the way,

111
00:07:04,200 --> 00:07:05,440
doesn't Mr. Hu like

112
00:07:05,460 --> 00:07:06,790
the braised beef I make?

113
00:07:07,050 --> 00:07:08,530
I'll prepare some more

114
00:07:08,560 --> 00:07:09,830
and bring it over to you.

115
00:07:09,830 --> 00:07:11,070
That's thoughtful of you.

116
00:07:11,070 --> 00:07:13,750
We haven't even finished
what you brought last time.

117
00:07:13,750 --> 00:07:14,750
Nie Yucheng

118
00:07:14,840 --> 00:07:16,400
is so lucky to have a wife

119
00:07:16,450 --> 00:07:18,010
like you.

120
00:07:19,680 --> 00:07:21,000
What are you talking about?

121
00:07:21,000 --> 00:07:22,240
So secretively.

122
00:07:22,360 --> 00:07:23,410
-Exactly.
-What?

123
00:07:23,470 --> 00:07:26,110
Are you afraid
we're gossiping about your Zhang?

124
00:07:26,110 --> 00:07:27,150
Stop it.

125
00:07:27,280 --> 00:07:28,190
Please, keep chatting.

126
00:07:28,190 --> 00:07:29,850
I need to use the restroom too.

127
00:07:36,000 --> 00:07:37,850
You didn't see how she was just now,

128
00:07:37,850 --> 00:07:40,250
acting so submissively for her husband.

129
00:07:40,270 --> 00:07:42,000
I felt sorry just watching her.

130
00:07:42,130 --> 00:07:43,830
Hasn't she found out about Nie Yucheng

131
00:07:43,830 --> 00:07:45,490
and that woman from Yuhua yet?

132
00:07:45,500 --> 00:07:47,430
It's already spread to our circle.

133
00:07:47,740 --> 00:07:49,570
Everyone knows about it.

134
00:07:50,120 --> 00:07:51,600
How could she not know?

135
00:07:52,460 --> 00:07:53,480
Maybe

136
00:07:53,480 --> 00:07:54,810
she's just pretending.

137
00:07:55,360 --> 00:07:57,760
What's so unusual
about this kind of thing?

138
00:07:58,060 --> 00:07:59,800
When a husband has a little affair or two,

139
00:07:59,800 --> 00:08:01,120
you just turn a blind eye

140
00:08:01,120 --> 00:08:02,450
and everything's fine.

141
00:08:02,720 --> 00:08:04,840
Especially in her situation.

142
00:08:04,870 --> 00:08:06,410
She doesn't even have a job.

143
00:08:06,800 --> 00:08:07,720
It's Nie Yucheng

144
00:08:07,720 --> 00:08:09,480
who makes money
to support their whole family.

145
00:08:09,480 --> 00:08:11,190
What could she possibly complain about?

146
00:08:11,190 --> 00:08:12,160
Would she dare

147
00:08:12,190 --> 00:08:14,190
to ask for a divorce?

148
00:08:14,190 --> 00:08:15,190
Exactly.

149
00:08:15,680 --> 00:08:17,510
If a woman who depends on her husband

150
00:08:17,510 --> 00:08:18,750
can't at least be this tolerant,

151
00:08:18,750 --> 00:08:19,610
how will she do?

152
00:08:26,720 --> 00:08:28,750
Mr. Ji, besides the hotels
we just discussed,

153
00:08:28,750 --> 00:08:30,000
Rongshe has also offered

154
00:08:30,000 --> 00:08:31,390
very generous terms.

155
00:08:31,390 --> 00:08:33,520
They're willing to give you 5% equity.

156
00:08:33,840 --> 00:08:34,600
Then...

157
00:08:35,320 --> 00:08:36,840
what about the Purong Hotel?

158
00:08:36,840 --> 00:08:39,299
Purong Hotel may be an old hotel
in Shanghai,

159
00:08:39,900 --> 00:08:42,360
but ever since Mr. Wei retired 6 years ago

160
00:08:42,640 --> 00:08:45,080
and his nephew Wei Siyuan
took over as general manager,

161
00:08:45,080 --> 00:08:47,470
it has been going downhill
year after year.

162
00:08:47,470 --> 00:08:48,620
Not only have there been
constant negative stories

163
00:08:48,620 --> 00:08:51,040
about financial scandals
and external crises,

164
00:08:51,040 --> 00:08:53,570
they also have not achieved
any real results.

165
00:08:54,120 --> 00:08:54,750
I don't think

166
00:08:54,750 --> 00:08:56,960
it's the best choice for you.

167
00:08:56,960 --> 00:08:58,630
Although their offer is generous

168
00:08:58,630 --> 00:09:00,710
and they promise you the position
of general manager,

169
00:09:00,710 --> 00:09:02,510
the conditions are quite harsh.

170
00:09:03,160 --> 00:09:04,240
What are these?

171
00:09:05,150 --> 00:09:06,390
The hotel has already sent
the relevant information

172
00:09:06,390 --> 00:09:07,630
to your email.

173
00:09:07,630 --> 00:09:09,510
You can take some time to review it.

174
00:09:09,510 --> 00:09:11,790
They're giving you one year
as general manager.

175
00:09:11,790 --> 00:09:12,960
Only if the hotel

176
00:09:12,960 --> 00:09:14,960
achieves over 30% profit growth
during that year

177
00:09:13,660 --> 00:09:14,560
[Inbox]

178
00:09:14,740 --> 00:09:16,390
[Mr. Ji Feng, we sincerely invite you to
serve as General Manager of Purong Hotel.]

179
00:09:15,270 --> 00:09:17,240
will the previously mentioned terms
take effect.

180
00:09:17,240 --> 00:09:18,240
And if it doesn't?

181
00:09:18,250 --> 00:09:21,290
[Sales Report of Purong Hotel]

182
00:09:18,870 --> 00:09:19,960
Then you leave.

183
00:09:20,600 --> 00:09:23,270
If you're considering
taking on such a difficult role,

184
00:09:23,270 --> 00:09:25,480
do you have any other conditions?

185
00:09:25,750 --> 00:09:26,390
After one year,

186
00:09:26,390 --> 00:09:28,840
I want 10% of Purong Hotel's shares.

187
00:09:30,750 --> 00:09:32,910
[Ningxin]

188
00:09:33,910 --> 00:09:34,770
Director Wang.

189
00:09:35,240 --> 00:09:36,100
Director Wang.

190
00:09:36,200 --> 00:09:37,000
Nie.

191
00:09:37,630 --> 00:09:38,440
Thank you so much

192
00:09:38,440 --> 00:09:41,480
for giving us the opportunity
with the Yufeng Jiangnan project.

193
00:09:41,480 --> 00:09:42,840
You don't need to thank me.

194
00:09:42,840 --> 00:09:44,440
I was just pressured

195
00:09:44,510 --> 00:09:46,110
by Zhen until I had no choice.

196
00:09:46,200 --> 00:09:47,270
If you want to thank someone,

197
00:09:47,270 --> 00:09:48,330
thank her instead.

198
00:09:48,570 --> 00:09:50,620
Zhen? You mean Lu Zhenzhen?

199
00:09:51,120 --> 00:09:52,830
Yes, she's my goddaughter.

200
00:09:54,910 --> 00:09:55,960
She never told you?

201
00:09:55,960 --> 00:09:56,770
No, she didn't.

202
00:09:56,770 --> 00:09:58,820
Her father and I are old classmates.

203
00:09:59,240 --> 00:10:01,060
This time, for your matter,

204
00:10:01,080 --> 00:10:03,170
goodness, she called me every day.

205
00:10:03,600 --> 00:10:05,200
I've never heard her

206
00:10:05,440 --> 00:10:07,640
speak to me in such a sweet voice before.

207
00:10:13,270 --> 00:10:13,840
Mr. Yang.

208
00:10:15,240 --> 00:10:15,840
Feng.

209
00:10:17,630 --> 00:10:18,480
Feng.

210
00:10:19,360 --> 00:10:20,320
Our Yuhua

211
00:10:20,320 --> 00:10:22,270
will need your and Mr. Nie's support
in the future.

212
00:10:22,270 --> 00:10:24,240
Please include us in any future projects.

213
00:10:24,240 --> 00:10:25,250
Don't mention it.

214
00:10:25,510 --> 00:10:26,480
We're old friends.

215
00:10:26,480 --> 00:10:27,080
Come on, bottoms up!

216
00:10:27,080 --> 00:10:27,540
Cheers.

217
00:10:27,720 --> 00:10:27,910
Here.

218
00:10:27,910 --> 00:10:28,240
Okay.

219
00:10:32,640 --> 00:10:33,310
Zhen.

220
00:10:33,790 --> 00:10:35,190
Why aren't you drinking?

221
00:10:35,290 --> 00:10:36,210
Yes, Zhen.

222
00:10:36,720 --> 00:10:38,290
You should toast to Feng too.

223
00:10:38,290 --> 00:10:39,740
Feng, my alcohol tolerance

224
00:10:39,740 --> 00:10:41,340
isn't very good, I'm afraid.

225
00:10:42,510 --> 00:10:43,570
Just have a little.

226
00:10:43,840 --> 00:10:44,840
Just as a gesture.

227
00:10:46,510 --> 00:10:47,040
Alright.

228
00:10:50,270 --> 00:10:50,730
Come on.

229
00:10:53,270 --> 00:10:55,200
Don't drink if you can't handle it.

230
00:10:56,240 --> 00:10:56,790
How about this?

231
00:10:56,790 --> 00:10:58,270
Mr. Feng, let me toast you.

232
00:10:58,270 --> 00:10:59,440
No, please don't.

233
00:10:59,440 --> 00:11:01,030
-Boss, we won't let her drink anymore.
-Mr. Nie.

234
00:11:01,030 --> 00:11:01,670
Come on.

235
00:11:01,750 --> 00:11:02,480
Have a seat.

236
00:11:04,700 --> 00:11:05,410
Sit.

237
00:11:06,360 --> 00:11:06,910
Sit.

238
00:11:08,360 --> 00:11:09,800
Waiter, bring another chair.

239
00:11:09,800 --> 00:11:11,130
And a few more drinks.

240
00:11:12,870 --> 00:11:13,790
Thank you for helping me.

241
00:11:13,790 --> 00:11:14,910
Let's drink.

242
00:11:14,910 --> 00:11:15,720
Let's drink.

243
00:11:34,950 --> 00:11:36,980
[Zhenhai District] [Hongkou District]

244
00:11:44,730 --> 00:11:45,930
Men change their hearts

245
00:11:45,930 --> 00:11:47,960
just like phone upgrades.

246
00:11:48,150 --> 00:11:49,720
It's perfectly normal.

247
00:11:50,120 --> 00:11:52,250
Especially in her situation.

248
00:11:52,330 --> 00:11:53,550
She doesn't even have a job.

249
00:11:53,550 --> 00:11:54,510
It's Nie Yucheng

250
00:11:54,510 --> 00:11:56,320
who makes money
to support their whole family.

251
00:11:56,320 --> 00:11:57,670
What could she possibly complain about?

252
00:11:57,670 --> 00:11:59,790
Would she dare to ask for a divorce?

253
00:11:59,810 --> 00:12:00,910
I, Nie Yucheng,

254
00:12:01,360 --> 00:12:02,920
have been working hard all this time

255
00:12:02,920 --> 00:12:04,050
for only one reason—

256
00:12:04,260 --> 00:12:05,070
you.

257
00:12:13,630 --> 00:12:13,980
[Minfu Bank]

258
00:12:14,000 --> 00:12:14,670
[Minfu Bank Expenditure]

259
00:12:14,690 --> 00:12:15,740
[Transfer via online banking: 150,000 RMB]

260
00:12:32,110 --> 00:12:34,080
Welcome home.

261
00:12:41,570 --> 00:12:43,640
I'm finally home.

262
00:12:44,350 --> 00:12:46,210
Nothing like the comfort of home.

263
00:12:53,780 --> 00:12:54,580
What's wrong?

264
00:12:55,000 --> 00:12:56,040
Have you been drinking?

265
00:12:56,040 --> 00:12:56,840
No, I haven't.

266
00:12:58,080 --> 00:12:59,440
I drove all the way back.

267
00:12:59,440 --> 00:13:00,600
How could I drink?

268
00:13:01,390 --> 00:13:03,200
Aren't you being a bit paranoid?

269
00:13:05,370 --> 00:13:06,240
Did Minghui...

270
00:13:07,080 --> 00:13:08,680
borrow money from you again?

271
00:13:10,020 --> 00:13:11,280
You mean that 150,000?

272
00:13:11,910 --> 00:13:12,480
Yes.

273
00:13:13,360 --> 00:13:15,240
He said his family urgently needs money

274
00:13:15,240 --> 00:13:16,730
and asked me for a temporary loan.

275
00:13:16,730 --> 00:13:17,490
I'm sorry.

276
00:13:18,270 --> 00:13:20,530
I lent it to him without asking you first.

277
00:13:21,120 --> 00:13:22,670
What happened with his family?

278
00:13:22,670 --> 00:13:23,660
Their family...

279
00:13:23,790 --> 00:13:25,840
Either his wife Ting has issues today

280
00:13:25,840 --> 00:13:27,900
