00:28:59,270 --> 00:29:01,800
the Xu Miyu who always reads your mood
and acts accordingly,

563
00:29:01,800 --> 00:29:03,720
who acts in front of your bosses
and colleagues

564
00:29:03,720 --> 00:29:05,550
as the perfect,

565
00:29:05,550 --> 00:29:06,750
understanding wife.

566
00:29:07,960 --> 00:29:09,310
But this Xu Miyu in front of you

567
00:29:09,310 --> 00:29:12,040
makes you feel like
you can't control her, right?

568
00:29:14,570 --> 00:29:15,470
Let me tell you.

569
00:29:16,110 --> 00:29:17,410
From today on,

570
00:29:17,850 --> 00:29:19,000
everything I do,

571
00:29:19,000 --> 00:29:20,160
every word I say,

572
00:29:20,160 --> 00:29:21,400
I won't be trying to please you anymore.

573
00:29:21,400 --> 00:29:23,440
I won't care if you're happy or not.

574
00:29:24,730 --> 00:29:25,810
I'll only care

575
00:29:26,400 --> 00:29:27,310
if I'm happy.

576
00:29:34,250 --> 00:29:35,290
Miss Lu.

577
00:29:36,040 --> 00:29:37,000
How's the baby?

578
00:29:38,800 --> 00:29:40,730
Did the prenatal check-up go well?

579
00:29:48,430 --> 00:29:49,360
Don't be afraid.

580
00:29:49,460 --> 00:29:51,460
I just want to take a good look at you.

581
00:29:54,240 --> 00:29:55,090
Indeed.

582
00:29:56,900 --> 00:29:57,900
Young,

583
00:29:58,670 --> 00:29:59,510
beautiful,

584
00:30:00,710 --> 00:30:01,790
cunning,

585
00:30:03,000 --> 00:30:04,400
and without principles.

586
00:30:05,420 --> 00:30:07,090
What's that saying again?

587
00:30:05,460 --> 00:30:06,570
[Celebration Banquet
for the Yufeng Jiangnan Project]

588
00:30:08,360 --> 00:30:11,620
The lower someone goes,
the more unstoppable they become.

589
00:30:12,160 --> 00:30:12,990
That's right.

590
00:30:14,070 --> 00:30:16,200
But your taste isn't very good.

591
00:30:17,190 --> 00:30:18,350
The person you've fallen for

592
00:30:18,350 --> 00:30:20,610
is a highly polished, self-serving man.

593
00:30:21,350 --> 00:30:24,660
If you're not even more calculating
than he is,

594
00:30:24,780 --> 00:30:25,680
I'm afraid

595
00:30:25,700 --> 00:30:26,880
it won't end well

596
00:30:28,070 --> 00:30:29,980
if you stay with him.

597
00:30:34,040 --> 00:30:35,430
Nie Yucheng, am I right?

598
00:30:35,580 --> 00:30:39,950
[Celebration Banquet
for the Yufeng Jiangnan Project]

599
00:30:36,480 --> 00:30:38,480
How many years have we been married?

600
00:30:39,120 --> 00:30:40,400
Ten years, right?

601
00:30:41,730 --> 00:30:43,210
Time flies.

602
00:30:44,450 --> 00:30:46,850
In the blink of an eye,
10 years have passed.

603
00:30:47,360 --> 00:30:48,570
Actually, I've always known

604
00:30:48,570 --> 00:30:50,460
that you're a selfish person.

605
00:30:50,720 --> 00:30:52,230
You said you had stomach problems,

606
00:30:52,230 --> 00:30:53,480
so I willingly

607
00:30:53,510 --> 00:30:55,640
became a housewife for 10 years,

608
00:30:55,880 --> 00:30:57,880
preparing meals for you,

609
00:30:57,900 --> 00:31:00,370
and supporting you every step of the way
as your career advanced.

610
00:31:00,370 --> 00:31:01,810
Do you know why?

611
00:31:03,970 --> 00:31:05,030
Because I love you.

612
00:31:05,140 --> 00:31:06,820
I love our family.

613
00:31:07,010 --> 00:31:09,000
Miyu, can we not do this he—

614
00:31:09,320 --> 00:31:11,740
Until I saw with my own eyes
how you trampled on my dignity

615
00:31:11,740 --> 00:31:13,530
with another woman.

616
00:31:16,630 --> 00:31:17,770
I came here today

617
00:31:19,110 --> 00:31:20,890
to reclaim

618
00:31:21,320 --> 00:31:22,820
the dignity I've lost,

619
00:31:25,850 --> 00:31:27,020
to reclaim the self

620
00:31:27,300 --> 00:31:29,780
that doesn't even exist in your eyes.

621
00:31:32,490 --> 00:31:33,540
Nie Yucheng,

622
00:31:34,810 --> 00:31:36,000
let's get divorced.

623
00:31:41,340 --> 00:31:43,770
[Celebration Banquet
for the Yufeng Jiangnan Project]

624
00:31:57,070 --> 00:31:57,840
Xu Miyu.

625
00:32:00,080 --> 00:32:00,990
Xu Miyu!

626
00:32:01,990 --> 00:32:03,500
