632
00:32:09,810 --> 00:32:11,210
Don't you want a divorce?

633
00:32:11,370 --> 00:32:12,890
What gives you the right to divorce me?

634
00:32:12,890 --> 00:32:14,660
What makes you think you can divorce me?

635
00:32:14,660 --> 00:32:16,490
Do you think you'll have a good life
after divorcing me?

636
00:32:16,490 --> 00:32:17,410
You won't!

637
00:32:17,550 --> 00:32:18,890
You're nothing but a parasite!

638
00:32:18,890 --> 00:32:20,550
Your whole family is the same!

639
00:32:27,960 --> 00:32:28,720
Xu Miyu!

640
00:32:30,700 --> 00:32:32,230
Let's see how far you can go!

641
00:32:33,140 --> 00:32:35,870
If you're so capable,
don't come back begging me!

642
00:32:49,360 --> 00:32:51,470
♪ I know at the start of every story ♪

643
00:32:52,430 --> 00:32:54,450
