648
00:33:09,710 --> 00:33:15,230
♪ Unfinished dreams hurt the most ♪

649
00:33:16,650 --> 00:33:18,470
♪ Like a moth drawn to the flame ♪

650
00:33:19,050 --> 00:33:22,280
♪ Wandering aimlessly
