654
00:33:26,070 --> 00:33:26,960
You won't!

655
00:33:26,330 --> 00:33:29,430
♪ Like fire that finally took my life ♪

656
00:33:30,010 --> 00:33:31,800
♪ I thought my deep devotion
and sincerity ♪

657
00:33:32,430 --> 00:33:34,090
♪ Would earn your eternal loyalty ♪

658
00:33:33,880 --> 00:33:35,160
You're nothing but a parasite!

659
00:33:34,530 --> 00:33:35,760
