715
00:36:04,400 --> 00:36:06,800
I've been working as a chef
at Purong Hotel.

716
00:36:09,340 --> 00:36:11,070
So your dream really came true?

717
00:36:11,510 --> 00:36:13,640
Working as a chef at a five-star hotel?

718
00:36:13,850 --> 00:36:14,550
That's wonderful.

719
00:36:14,550 --> 00:36:15,880
I'm just the sous-chef.

720
00:36:17,190 --> 00:36:19,670
But if you stayed at our hotel this year,

721
00:36:19,690 --> 00:36:22,090
you might have actually tasted my cooking.

722
00:36:25,630 --> 00:36:26,940
Listen to me rambling.

723
00:36:27,360 --> 00:36:28,760
You have your own house here.

724
00:36:28,760 --> 00:36:30,490
Why would you stay at our hotel?

725
00:36:35,760 --> 00:36:36,760
Where do you live?

726
00:36:36,810 --> 00:36:38,070
I rented an apartment.

727
00:36:38,070 --> 00:36:39,470
It's not far from Purong.

728
00:36:41,260 --> 00:36:43,120
The rent must be expensive there.

729
00:36:43,360 --> 00:36:45,230
Not really. I live alone,

730
00:36:45,260 --> 00:36:46,730
spending my own money as I please.

731
00:36:46,730 --> 00:36:47,930
You're still single?

732
00:36:48,630 --> 00:36:49,890
I prefer being single.

733
00:36:50,070 --> 00:36:52,400
Another person just complicates things.

734
00:36:54,630 --> 00:36:55,510
I shouldn't be

735
00:36:55,510 --> 00:36:56,960
putting these toxic ideas in your head.

736
00:36:56,960 --> 00:36:58,500
You're so family-oriented.

737
00:36:58,500 --> 00:37:01,160
You should go home
and take care of your husband.

738
00:37:11,190 --> 00:37:11,920
Qiaoqi.

739
00:37:12,960 --> 00:37:14,150
Thank you for today.

740
00:37:14,560 --> 00:37:17,150
It's so wonderful to see you again.

741
00:37:17,340 --> 00:37:19,080
